Midterm details
by sinan kalkan - Wednesday, April 2, 2025, 11:14 PM
 	
Dear all,

I hope everyone is doing well and using the break effectively. 

I would like to remind you that we will have the midterm exam on 7 April, Monday at 17:40.

Location: Will be announced later.
Coverage: The midterm exam will cover all topics until and including Week 6.
Type of the exam: Closed-notes. Includes (i) questions requiring Mathematical derivations for forward pass as well as backward pass for a given network, (ii) questions on fundamental concepts or methods, and (iii) [probably] designing a network for a given problem description. 
Duration: Not decided yet but expect it to be around 120 minutes. 
